This code help to get detail information about Books with cover page. The information are retry from Amazon API.

Download the app from Github

1. unzip the app
2. run it inside your apache "htdocs" folder

Please do use attached public key & private key. please sign up a key from amazon api from this url http://aws.amazon.com/fws/

After signup go to "Security Credentials" in "Account" section and there you can create access key etc.
// public key
  var $publicKey = "xxxxxxxxxxxxxx";
	// private key
	var $privateKey = "xxxxxxxxxxxxxx";
